text:
{
  "prompt": "A quarter-class electric motorcycle designed in the style of the Honda Zoomer e-scooter shown. The design includes a minimalist, exposed frame with military green body panels and matte black mechanical parts. Features include a central hub motor, mid-size radiator for liquid cooling (inspired by car antifreeze systems), a comfortable seat with a lumbar backrest, a 20-inch front wheel and a 16-inch rear wheel. The front uses inverted suspension forks, and the rear features a mono shock. The overall structure is low-slung and compact but muscular, without exterior fairings, showcasing its internal structure. Urban commuter aesthetics with performance-oriented proportions.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Design of a quarter-class electric motorcycle inspired by the Honda Zoomer e-style. The bike features a minimalist, naked scooter frame with a matte black chassis and military green panels. It has a large 20-inch front wheel and a 16-inch rear wheel for stability and performance. The front suspension is telescopic, while the rear includes a dual-shock system. No front cowl is used, showcasing exposed handlebars and a round LED headlamp. The seat is single-rider with a backrest for ergonomic support. Battery is embedded under the foot platform with a central motor drive, giving it a futuristic but rugged appearance.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A concept electric motorcycle inspired by the design of the Honda Cub EV shown, but upgraded to quarter-liter class (250cc equivalent). Maintain the minimalist, clean red and white frame design with a step-through structure and compact body. Enhance with thicker tires, larger front and rear disc brakes, a robust suspension system, and a slightly more aggressive stance. Emphasize performance elements while keeping the lightweight, urban-friendly look of the original.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A modified Honda Cub-style electric motorcycle shown in high resolution against a white background. The design keeps a minimalist and clean look. The bike is equipped with a 3000W central motor. The original muffler is removed, revealing a clean rear section. The bodywork is free of plastic fairings (no cowls), showing a raw frame structure. The design retains the iconic red and white paint scheme and step-through frame, with modern black alloy wheels and disc brakes.",
  "size": "1152x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A modern electric motorcycle in red and white color scheme with a step-through frame. The design removes all gas components: no fuel tank, no engine block, and no exhaust/muffler. It features a mid-drive 3000W electric motor housed neatly within the central frame. The frame is exposed with no side fairings or cowling, and it has a minimalistic, futuristic look with clean lines. The seat is flat and ergonomic, handlebars are straight and clean, and the wheels are large with disc brakes. Captured in a clean studio environment on a white background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A modern, step-through electric motorcycle in red and white, designed without a top tube and without a traditional fuel tank. It features a central motor drive (3000W class), exposed frame design, black alloy wheels, large front and rear disc brakes, and a minimalist headlight and handlebar configuration. The style is clean and futuristic, suitable for urban commuting, shown from a side view against a white background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution digital rendering of a modern electric motorcycle designed with the motor and battery integrated into a single compact central unit. The bike has no fuel tank or exhaust, with a minimalist frame in red and black, open step-through design (no top tube), and clean, futuristic styling. The wheels are thick and durable, with disc brakes and a sporty yet urban appearance. Photographed in a studio on a soft white background, the motorcycle's seamless integration of drivetrain components is the focal point.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution side profile of a modern electric motorcycle with a clean, minimalist design. The bike features a red and white color scheme with black detailing. The unique design integrates both the motor and the battery into a single compact unit located entirely beneath the floorboard (footrest) area, creating an open and low-slung frame above. The motorcycle has no visible fuel tank or exhaust, emphasizing its electric nature. It has wide black wheels, disc brakes, and a slim seat with a slightly retro headlamp and mirrors, set against a plain white studio background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A technical cutaway illustration of a red and white electric scooter, showing a transparent side view of the internal battery pack installed under the floorboard and seat. The 72V 120Ah battery pack is compactly arranged in two layers, with visible cylindrical cells (21700 type) and wiring routed neatly. The motor is integrated into the lower frame area. The background is plain white and the design is clean, technical, and detailed like an engineering drawing.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
